# About this collection

The API under this collection includes four artifacts **{Environment, Flight, Motor and Rocket}** with 6 endpoints each covering artifact **creation, reading, editing, deleting, simulating and retrieving artifact as jsonpickle string.**

- POST `api/artifact/{{artifact_id}}` { message, artifact_id }

- GET `api/artifact/{{artifact_id}}` { Artifact }

- GET `api/rocketpy/artifact/{{artifact_id}}` { json_pickle_string_artifact }

- GET `api/simulate/artifact/{{artifact_id}}` { ArtifactSimulationSummary }

- PUT `api/artifact/{{artifact_id}}` { message, new_artifact_id }

- DELETE `api/artifact/{{artifact_id}}` { deleted_artifact_id, message }


**Flight artifact** have also additional routes that allows to update its own artifacts.

- POST `api/flight/{{flight_id}}/artifact/` { message, flight_id }


## **Using this collection**

- Run this collection by clicking on "Run".


